Please also generate for a $topic$ site a simple JSON structure with the following mask: '{"titleAndText":{"title":"<title>","text":"<text>"}}' and fill up with relevant descriptive content (minimum 100 words) of the site topic for $page$ page.
Content should be translated to $lang$ language.
If you are generating same context page topic please generate new content not similar you've just generated to same prompt request. Usually this will be 3 total requests on the same page topic.
Important: if you can't access the content of specific web pages or external databases please create an exemplar JSON structure with hypothetical content that might be suitable for a context page you are generating.
Response in JSON only, no formatting, plain JSON text, even you can' perform the request, please answer in JSON format of corresponding mask defined in the beginning of this prompt.
